<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>FOR SALE</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%- facebook_og.each_pair do |key, value| %>
    <meta property="og:<%= key %>" content="<%= value.gsub('"', "'") %>" />
  <% end %>
</head>
<body>
  <div class='ui page grid'>
    <div class="row">
      <main class="column" id="content">
        <h1 class="ui block header">FOR SALE: Motorsports Registration Software</h1>
        <div class="ui segment">
          <p>
            This software is available for purchase. Please click "Contact Sales" below to discuss.
          </p>

          <ul class="ui list">
            <li class="item">Registration and payment system for endurance motorsports events</li>
            <li class="item">RFID-powered pit stop timing &amp; Driver identification</li>
            <li class="item">Class-leading live event integration</li>
            <li class="item">Driver-name injection into RaceMonitor feeds</li>
            <li class="item">Integrated text-message support to contact teams, drivers, and event participants</li>
            <li class="item">Driver stint analysis, attributed to each individual driver</li>
            <li class="item">Ability to track laps driven by each driver</li>
            <li class="item">Integrates directly with Orbits timing system</li>
            <li class="item">Grid sheet generation</li>
            <li class="item">Results calculation and display, supports event and season-long results tracking</li>
            <li class="item">Violation tracking system to track event incidents attributed to team or driver</li>
            <li class="item">Backup scanning system can use barcode scanner in case of RFID failure (Recommend barcode printed on your RFID tags)</li>
            <li class="item">API to support mobile app integration (Including live pit timing)</li>
            <li class="item">Training and support available</li>
            <li class="item">Exclusive options available</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="ui list">
            <div class="item">
              <a href="/info_sheet.docx" class="ui small basic button">
                Download Info Sheet
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <a href="mailto:nhance@reenhanced.com?subject=race+software+purchase" class="ui huge primary button">
                Contact Sales
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>



        <div class="ui divider hidden"></div>
        <div class="ui segments">
          <div class="ui secondary segment center aligned">
            Website designed, developed, hosted, and maintained by <a href="http://www.reenhanced.com/">Reenhanced</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
